title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Using simBrief with flybywire A32NX
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to plan a flight using simBrief and load it directly into our airplane using the flybywire A32NX addon for Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020.

AS320NX can be downloaded from this site: https://flybywiresim.com/a32nx

The tool used to plan our flight simBrief can be found here: https://www.simbrief.com
